summary: Adds 20 new eye textures to the game.
descriptionHtml:
[center]﻿[/center][size=4][color=#e06666]I have been wanting to do this for awhile as I have used these in a previous mod and liked them. And even contacted JU5TPeachy for permissions a year ago but kept putting it off or was too lazy.  Even tho they were free to use I still contacted the author with my idea. As you can see the premise of these textures is focused on multi-color designs. The work is very detailed and a breath of fresh air for character creation and a modders resource to use in follower or NPC projects. The eyes currently are only for Male and Female [/color][color=#ea9999]Human[/color][color=#e06666] and [/color][color=#ea9999]Elven[/color][color=#e06666] races. [/color]

[color=#ffff00]Note: The lovely model in the first screenie is using Moonlit Sea.
[/color][/size]

[color=#ffd966][size=4]Credit goes to these authors for their blood, sweat, and tears. [/size][/color]

[url=https://www.deviantart.com/ju5tpeachy]Hand Painted Eye Textures by JU5TPeachy[/url]

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722?tab=description]The Eyes Of Beauty by LogRaam[/url]
author: Kittyness
